    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Cloning With Intent</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Nicole Lanouette letter says it is pointless to clone animals near extinction (Oct 9 article) if their habitats are being destroyed</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Cloning Used in an Effort to Preserve Rare Species'' (news article, Oct. 9): I hope that this promising new technology gives us bolstered incentive to protect ecosystems instead of cause for apathy.  After all, what good have we done if we preserve species but leave them homeless?</p>
        <p>NICOLE LANOUETTE  New York, Oct. 9, 2000</p>
      </block>
